text: "Keep On Movin'" is a 1999 song by British boy band Five and is the second single from their second studio album Invincible. It went to number 1 in the United Kingdom, Hungary and Scotland, number 2 in Ireland and Italy, number 5 in the Netherlands, number 6 in Australia, Belgium, Finland and Spain, number 7 in New Zealand, number 9 in Denmark, number 10 in Sweden and number 20 in Ireland. ==Track listings== UK and Australian CD1 # "Keep On Movin'" # "Inspector Gadget" # Enhanced CD UK and Australian CD2 # "Keep On Movin'" # "How Do Ya Feel" (Biffco remix) # "Reminiscing" UK cassette single and European CD single # "Keep On Movin'" # "Inspector Gadget" European maxi-CD single # "Keep On Movin'" # "How Do Ya Feel" # "Reminiscing" # "Inspector Gadget" # Enhanced CD ==References== Category:1999 songs Category:Five (group) songs
